---
// EDGE - The EmotionOS for Human Connection
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>EDGE | The EmotionOS</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-black text-zinc-100 font-sans antialiased">
    
    <header class="fixed top-0 w-full flex justify-between items-center px-8 py-6 z-50 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-zinc-900">
      <div class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase italic">EDGE</div>
      <nav class="hidden md:flex gap-10 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-zinc-500">
        <a href="#vision" class="hover:text-fuchsia-500 transition-colors">Vision</a>
        <a href="#tech" class="hover:text-fuchsia-500 transition-colors">The Tech</a>
        <a href="#privacy" class="hover:text-fuchsia-500 transition-colors">Privacy</a>
      </nav>
      <button class="px-6 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full border border-zinc-800 hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all">
        Investor Deck
      </button>
    </header>

    <main class="relative min-h-screen pt-32 px-6">
      <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center mb-32">
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-[0.9]">
          THE <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-500 to-cyan-400">EMOTION OS</span> <br /> 
          FOR HUMAN CONNECTION.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-zinc-400 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
          Bridging the millennia-old <span class="text-white italic">Pleasure Gap</span>[cite: 37, 38]. We decode physiological signals into real-time guidance for synchronized intimacy[cite: 5, 14].
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4 mb-20">
          <input type="email" placeholder="access@edge.sex" class="w-full sm:w-80 px-6 py-4 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 focus:outline-none focus:border-fuchsia-500 transition-colors text-white" />
          <button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-black font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-fuchsia-500 hover:text-white transition-all shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)]">
            Join the Pilot
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="relative w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto h-4 bg-zinc-900 rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-zinc-800">
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 h-full w-40 -translate-x-1/2 bg-fuchsia-500/20 blur-sm"></div>
            <div class="absolute left-[48%] top-0 h-full w-1 bg-white shadow-[0_0_15px_#fff] animate-pulse"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-600 uppercase font-bold">Locking into the Pleasure Zone [cite: 49, 56]</p>
      </section>

      <section id="vision" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 py-24 border-t border-zinc-900">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The Data-Driven <br/>Movement [cite: 12, 32]</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">Modern intimacy relies on guesswork. EDGE transforms wearables into an intelligent interface, translating HRV and GSR signals into actionable feedback[cite: 12, 14].</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">By quantifying empathy and synchrony, we aim to reshape the architecture of human communication[cite: 33].</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800">
            <h3 class="text-fuchsia-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-4">Core Mechanic [cite: 18]</h3>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Time in Zone [cite: 18]</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">Quantifying session success by the duration partners sustain peak mutual pleasure states[cite: 18, 56]. Communication becomes obsolete—the data does the talking[cite: 54].</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="privacy" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-24 border-t border-zinc-900 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-zinc-600 mb-8">Privacy by Design [cite: 24, 55]</h2>
        <p class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-12 italic text-zinc-200 uppercase tracking-tighter">AES-256 Encryption. <br/>Local Differential Privacy[cite: 23, 55, 56].</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Only anonymized feature vectors leave the device[cite: 56]. We maintain global regulatory readiness under "wellness communication" standards[cite: 24, 60].
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="py-12 border-t border-zinc-900 text-center text-[10px] text-zinc-700 tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
        © 2026 EDGE | The EmotionOS for Human Connection [cite: 20]
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
